# .gitmessage
# This file defines the default commit message template for this repository.
# Usage: The LLM should use the following format for commit messages:
#
# <component>: <short description>
#
# Examples:
# n8n: Fix namespaces
# ollama: Added Only deepseek-r1:1.5b
# jellyfin: Update deployment image
# rook-ceph: Enable new storage class
#
# For model additions, specify the model name and version clearly:
# ollama: Added Only <model-name>:<version>
#
# Please provide a concise, clear summary of the change after the colon.
#
# Optionally, add more details below the summary if needed.

<component>: <short description>

# Details (optional):
# - Motivation
# - Impact
# - Related issues or PRs
